Module nwalters.inventorytrackingsystemproject

Class ProductAddControllerScreen

java.lang.Object
nwalters.inventorytrackingsystemproject.ProductAddControllerScreen
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ProductAddControllerScreen extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class controls the data for the ProductAddForm.fxml. This allows the user to add a product and add the appropriate data to the table. This also allows the user to add parts to the product.
